This paper discusses the selection of the best classification algorithm for a given dataset, which is a common problem in machine learning. The paper focuses on the evaluation of performance measures for classifiers comparison, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
